    <figure>
      <img src="img/strategy-logo.png" alt="">
    </figure>
    <article>
      <h2>Within a day</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Almost all of the nicotine is out of your bloodstream.</li>
        <li>The level of carbon monoxide in your blood drops to normal.</li>
        <li>Oxygen can more easily reach your heart and muscles.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </li>
  <li>
    <figure>
      <img src="img/strategy-logo.png" alt="">
    </figure>
    <article>
