      <ul>
        <li>Your coughing and wheezing decrease.</li>
        <li>Your immune system is beginning its recovery so your body is better at fighting off infection.</li>
        <li>Your blood is less thick and sticky and blood flow to your hands and feet has improved.</li>
       </ul>
    </article>
  </li>
  <li>
    <figure>
      <img src="img/strategy-logo.png" alt="">
    </figure>
